NOTIFICATION.Text:
Special SAP Upgrade Startup
After upgrade team has verified that SAP upgrade is complete, verify with Bethel that the agents have been updated. Then manually execute SAP.SYSTEM.BOUNCE.EXTENDED.SUNDAY.SAP.UPGRADE.PT2
